snippet.title: What is League of Legends?
snippet.description:
Welcome to League of Legends! Sign up for a free account at http://riot.com/signup

This is a short tutorial on how to play League. If you're a new player, this guide will help get you up to speed. 

If you're a veteran player, consider sharing this with a friend who wants to learn!
